## 🔧 What You Need To Do Next

### **Backend Endpoints To Implement**

See `BACKEND_INTEGRATION.md` for exact code, but here's the checklist:

**✅ Already Working:**
- POST /auth/register
- POST /auth/login
- GET /auth/me
- POST /lessons/upload

**❌ Need To Add:**
- GET /classes (fetch teacher's classes)
- POST /classes (create new class)
- PUT /classes/:id (update class)
- DELETE /classes/:id (delete class)
- GET /students?classId=X (fetch students)
- POST /students (add student)
- DELETE /students/:id (remove student)
- GET /notifications (fetch alerts)
- PUT /teachers/profile (update teacher info)
- PUT /teachers/password (change password)

