## 🐛 Common Issues & Solutions

**Problem:** "Failed to fetch classes"
**Solution:** Make sure backend is running on port 8000 and CORS is enabled

**Problem:** "Invalid token" error
**Solution:** Your JWT expired (default 7 days). Just log out and log back in

**Problem:** Sidebar doesn't update after creating a class
**Solution:** Call `sidebar.update()` after modifying `State.classes`

**Problem:** AI command does nothing
**Solution:** The backend `/voice/process` endpoint isn't implemented yet—it's a placeholder

---

